{"tid":552301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"真子公主結婚驚爆延期！「準婆婆包養男友」醜聞曝光","createTime":"2018-02-06T11:34:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-07T05:48:10.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"95ff2166b0d5fc7e5f6d550cd6ca27ebdc5be14a","tid":552301,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"日本皇室真子公主結婚驚爆延期！她是秋篠宮夫婦的長女，原本和大學同學小室圭於2017年9月召開記者會，甜蜜宣布訂婚，婚禮定在年底11月4日，皇家大喜受到全國民眾高度關注，沒想到傳出要延後至2020年！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2942/d2942540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2942%2Fd2942540.jpg&h=150df037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲日本皇室真子公主、小室圭結婚延期。<br />\n<br />\n據日雜《女性SEVEN》報導，小室圭和真子公主訂下婚姻一夕爆紅，大學曾為觀光擔任「海王子」，加上帥氣外型受到全世界傳媒關注。他現在任職法律事務所，按照原本行程，3月4日要舉行「納采之儀」，緊接著11月4日舉行結婚，不過儀式一口氣要延後2年，前所未有的延期決定引發揣測，關係者透露，「結婚儀式需要花時間籌備」，加上2019年天皇退位，新天皇繼位等，皇室相關的儀式太緊密，所以結婚才會被往後延。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2527/d2527235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2527%2Fd2527235.jpg&h=c59b78d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲真子公主和大學同學小室圭訂婚，轟動全國。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，小室圭的「異狀」也引起關注。他傳出1月下旬就病倒在床，疑似是家族的過去被挖出。他的父親小室敏勝2002年自殺，母親佳代被爆包養金雕師男友，媽媽曾收下外商男日幣400萬元（約台幣108萬元）、並一度有婚約，取消婚約後又和外商男為此發生欠債糾紛，有關這段醜聞對公主結婚是否造成壞影響，對此宮內廳曾回應：「沒有立場回答這個問題。」不過外界仍質疑的確對婚事造成影響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img-s-msn-com.akamaized.net/tenant/amp/entityid/AAuCAQC.img?h=400&amp;w=600&amp;m=6&amp;q=60&amp;o=f&amp;l=f&amp;x=247&amp;y=144\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg-s-msn-com.akamaized.net%2Ftenant%2Famp%2Fentityid%2FAAuCAQC.img%3Fh%3D400%26w%3D600%26m%3D6%26q%3D60%26o%3Df%26l%3Df%26x%3D247%26y%3D144&h=8aa6a623&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朱千雪坦承對Justin有感覺。<br />\n<br />\n真子公主、小室圭6日晚間聯名發表聲明，吐露現在心情，「我想我們很多事情太急了。」兩人在聲明中表示，一直以來為了結婚儀式、結婚後的生活不斷和雙親、相關人士討論，但是覺得秋天結婚沒有時間充分做準備，「很多事情都太快了，這個速度適不適合自己，要重新慎重考慮」，宣布結婚結果又無法實現，「是我們不夠成熟。」"},{"pid":"7cb0110b91602dd36ab8b59e5e24ec1798718b0e","tid":552301,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"咩係金鵰師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710c20e16e6bc07f2b03570b30c4f448017cc278","tid":552301,"uid":52605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:43:22.000Z","msg":"結咗婚冇咗公主身份<br />\n又要脱離皇族"},{"pid":"55544ff878edbf0b841374a03c2afb362960fe49","tid":552301,"uid":48796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"奶奶私生活唔符合大眾期望又要畀人講，噉搞法唔知結唔結到婚，個新郎都好撚無辜"},{"pid":"1d98071edb35736e4f8a6c7470d4cdbb12e968fc","tid":552301,"uid":57286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7cb0110b91602dd36ab8b59e5e24ec1798718b0e","tid":552301,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"咩係金鵰師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T11:52:43.000Z","msg":"金槍不倒大鵰男"},{"pid":"fbca760af19d6f982b3b16288eb0f819e11ba8c6","tid":552301,"uid":3773,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T12:01:00.000Z","msg":"真子&amp;愛子留返畀你哋<br />\n我要佳子就夠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33733456a6c994ae4423219df7a9a189740e9ffb","tid":552301,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上一代既事關佢地咩事"},{"pid":"cf7a091437fb013504ebe5100b584cbc45ad8f61","tid":552301,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T04:53:06.000Z","msg":"條仔個樣好奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d416d7f62a8f4907dfbb12d2b802d724cb1233c0","tid":552301,"uid":153497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"曾志偉係外商男？"},{"pid":"811da18006eb7263130c7df30a1cb6ccd9e8e119","tid":552301,"uid":75137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"女有錢過男就叫包養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"a773ad5ab8518d62dd1b5ba2ce5b331ee2de8e9e","tid":552301,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}